 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the Team GB star has recorded a leading round in the dressage team final.\", \"from\": 7374, \"to\": 7451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Moody told the BBC: \\\"Two weeks ago I was expecting to come for a lovely 10-day holiday in France, to be inspired, learn, and go home better.\", \"from\": 7453, \"to\": 7593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7453, \"end\": 7458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\", \"score\": 0.9999170216692619, \"rank\": 4.720952204982838e-05, \"text\": \"Moody\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\"}, {\"begin\": 7468, \"end\": 7471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9999882152781997, \"rank\": 1.1781586484264148e-05, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 7543, \"end\": 7549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9966708274952519, \"rank\": 0.0033402929162861333, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having to do this, there is been a bit of nausea but it's been an amazing experience with an incredible team around me.\\\"\", \"from\": 7595, \"to\": 7716, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB star Jeremiah Azu was disqualified from his heat in the men's 100m sprint at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 7718, \"to\": 7816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7731, \"end\": 7743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah_Azu\", \"score\": 0.9999990537376037, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeremiah Azu\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah_Azu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah_Azu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A false start was called after the 23-year-old was deemed to have gone too early.\", \"from\": 7818, \"to\": 7899, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Azu claimed he had been prompted to start by a noise from the pole vault event happening over on the other side of the stadium.\", \"from\": 7901, \"to\": 8028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said:  \\\"I am feeling great, so it's a shame.\", \"from\": 8030, \"to\": 8077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of crowd noise, the pole vault's going on, and I reacted to the sound [of that- and they are saying I can not run under protest, so I am going to go back to the team and, hopefully, they can sort it out.\", \"from\": 8079, \"to\": 8298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They said maybe I can run by myself after, but, yeah, I am just going to wait it out and see.\", \"from\": 8300, \"to\": 8394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's an Olympic crowd, they are so excited.\", \"from\": 8396, \"to\": 8440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not fault them, but we are on the start line and somebody's reacted to something that's going on [in the pole vault] and it set me off - so I am going to see what happens now.\\\"\", \"from\": 8441, \"to\": 8622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's another gold for Team GB!\", \"from\": 8626, \"to\": 8656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's eight team had a little wobble at the very start but powered through to win in over a second.\", \"from\": 8658, \"to\": 8761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE HERE  The women's eight team have won silver in the rowing.\", \"from\": 8763, \"to\": 8832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They comfortably beat Australia into fourth but were unable to pip Canada into second.\", \"from\": 8834, \"to\": 8920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8856, \"end\": 8865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999839901649, \"rank\": 1.5408684993515527e-08, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 8901, \"end\": 8907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9248051364628411, \"rank\": 0.08109204646017783, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dominant Romania won the race by a staggering four seconds.\", \"from\": 8922, \"to\": 8981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The dressage team Grand Prix final is underway in Paris.\", \"from\": 8983, \"to\": 9039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9001, \"end\": 9011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Prix_motorcycle_racing\", \"score\": 0.7757123336944945, \"rank\": 0.2881457325373326, \"text\": \"Grand Prix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Prix_motorcycle_racing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Prix_motorcycle_racing\"}, {\"begin\": 9033, \"end\": 9038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2730320749304394e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB will be going for a medal.\", \"from\": 9041, \"to\": 9075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9041, \"end\": 9048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3485674604637953e-22, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France boss Thierry Henry was unhappy with Enzo Millot's red card in Les Bleus' Olympics win over Argentina.\", \"from\": 9077, \"to\": 9185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9077, \"end\": 9083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9966708274952519, \"rank\": 0.0033402929162861333, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 9089, \"end\": 9102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thierry Henry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\"}, {\"begin\": 9120, \"end\": 9131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enzo_Millot\", \"score\": 0.9999983397397185, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Enzo Millot\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enzo_Millot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enzo_Millot\"}, {\"begin\": 9175, \"end\": 9184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8393730884622245, \"rank\": 0.19136533412742207, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A mass brawl broke out after full-time, with Millot red-carded.\", \"from\": 9187, \"to\": 9250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not agree with what happened at the end of the match.\", \"from\": 9252, \"to\": 9311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My player [Millot] got a red card and I do not accept it, it should not happen,\\\" Henry said.\", \"from\": 9312, \"to\": 9404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not control what happened.\", \"from\": 9406, \"to\": 9441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I went to greet the coach and when I turned around, what happened, happened.\", \"from\": 9442, \"to\": 9518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We won, but I did not like what happened at the end with my player.\\\"\", \"from\": 9519, \"to\": 9587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE HERE  Surfing judge Ben Lowe has been sent home from Paris for taking an 'inappropriate' photo with competitors.\", \"from\": 9589, \"to\": 9711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9619, \"end\": 9627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Lowe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ben Lowe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Lowe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Lowe\"}, {\"begin\": 9652, \"end\": 9657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2730320749304394e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lowe was captured posing and smiling with fellow Aussies Ethan Ewing and Bede Durbidge - who were competing in the events he was officiating.\", \"from\": 9713, \"to\": 9854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9786, \"end\": 9799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bede_Durbidge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bede Durbidge\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bede_Durbidge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bede_Durbidge\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The snap was shared toInstagramwith the caption: \\\"These three Straddie [Stradbroke Island] Boys doing their stuff at the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 9856, \"to\": 9987, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Surfing Association has now sent Lowe home.\", \"from\": 9989, \"to\": 10050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9993, \"end\": 10026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Surfing Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A statement read: \\\"It is inappropriate for a judge to be interacting in this manner with an athlete and their team.\\\"\", \"from\": 10052, \"to\": 10168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 10172, \"to\": 10281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 10282, \"to\": 10358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 10359, \"to\": 10391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Imane Khelif's father insists criticism of his daughter's presence in the Olympic boxing event has been 'immoral'.\", \"from\": 10392, \"to\": 10530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10416, \"end\": 10428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's participation has caused widespread debate.\", \"from\": 10532, \"to\": 10584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old boxer has higher testosterone levels than the average woman, prompting her to be banned from last year's World Championship.\", \"from\": 10585, \"to\": 10725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Italian opponent Angela Carini withdrew from their first-round fight after only 46 seconds, claiming she had never been punched so hard in her career.\", \"from\": 10727, \"to\": 10877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10727, \"end\": 10734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9998270325134896, \"rank\": 0.0001584929937607007, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 10744, \"end\": 10757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103664941, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Amar Khelife has now told critics: \\\"The attacks against her are immoral, it is not fair.\", \"from\": 10879, \"to\": 10971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Imane is a little girl that has loved sport since she was six-years-old, she used to play football.\", \"from\": 10973, \"to\": 11073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These critics and rumours aim to destabilise Imane, they do not want her to be the champion of the world.\", \"from\": 11075, \"to\": 11181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I tell her prove them wrong in the ring and I hope that she will honour Algeria and Arabic countries and win the gold medal.\", \"from\": 11183, \"to\": 11308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11256, \"end\": 11263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6928789265755486, \"rank\": 0.44325350582958967, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\